{"tid":2072903,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無一間銀行做到 一登記即有錢？","createTime":"2020-06-21T03:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T06:17:43.000Z","uid":51346,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa872614430f7f854228762f71e2feeb85452073","tid":2072903,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"實大把新客喎<br />\n到時唔合資格咪當個客借咗錢 逼佢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede877cfe74a50ddaeb50298e0e95dbd5a61169a","tid":2072903,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff05f903f531dc7d319bd847be000332a2a78d","tid":2072903,"uid":215700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"到時一百萬人同時攞一萬cash出嚟 <br />\n銀行都幾頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da96b395fe77cc20250d1897cd7a16d6f5ce57fd","tid":2072903,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ff05f903f531dc7d319bd847be000332a2a78d","tid":2072903,"uid":215700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"到時一百萬人同時攞一萬cash出嚟 <br />\n銀行都幾頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"銀行再問其他銀行借<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b947a79345cfa8a084d3a07889521c725d26ae6","tid":2072903,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"（一）會否提高每名成年香港永久性居民可獲發的現金款額至兩萬元，並與銀行界合作，<span style=\"color: red;\">容許銀行接獲個人客戶已簽妥的授權文件及核實其領取資格後，先行墊支發放該筆款項，以解市民燃眉之急</span>；如會，詳情為何；如否，原因為何；<br />\n<br />\n（一）財政司司長於《財政預算案》中宣布推出的現金發放計劃（計劃）將向每名年滿18歲的香港永久性居民發放一萬元，以鼓勵和帶動本地消費，同時紓緩市民的經濟壓力，預計約700萬人受惠。就該計劃的發放金額，我們在通盤考慮所有逆周期及紓緩措施和相關財政影響後，認為一萬元是合適的數目。計劃的籌備工作已進入最後階段，我們會盡快向市民公布詳情。我們現時的目標是爭取於六月底開始接受登記，並於七月內開始發放款項。估計700萬合資格市民大部分可在八月底前收到款項。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">x議員在問題中提及的方案，同樣須獲當事人授權使用其個人資料，以及核實有關市民的資格，施行上不會加快發放款項的時間。</span></span>"},{"pid":"8868d603ba075f4ba7d9a8a375788d1f656508d1","tid":2072903,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"咁多人報錯/假資料<br />\n始終都要望下掛"},{"pid":"d05ec79b1aa70246015ab031ffa9f06c1003c439","tid":2072903,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"銀行都唔會個個客都想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9261dc149187ad7a305dd99e0c916955a8eabe92","tid":2072903,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d05ec79b1aa70246015ab031ffa9f06c1003c439","tid":2072903,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"銀行都唔會個個客都想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"揀客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde4f2c89284844325a951463eb3f6db0bc1a6be","tid":2072903,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9261dc149187ad7a305dd99e0c916955a8eabe92","tid":2072903,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d05ec79b1aa70246015ab031ffa9f06c1003c439","tid":2072903,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"銀行都唔會個個客都想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"揀客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"好出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}